{"tid":2506143,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Jeff Bezos投訴SpaceX獨得NASA 28.9億美元合約  Elon Musk留言嘲笑","createTime":"2021-04-27T06:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T07:48:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5721723340126d7911d2d7465d3f66f080c31114","tid":2506143,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕特斯拉執行長馬斯克的太空公司「SpaceX」上週打敗亞馬遜執行長貝佐斯旗下太空公司「藍色起源（Blue Origin）」等競爭對手，獲NASA「阿提米絲」計畫（Artemis）大約，藍色起源不滿投訴，馬斯克對此狠酸貝佐斯的公司硬不起來。<br />\n<br />\n「SpaceX」、「藍色起源」、Dynetics等太空公司，競標NASA價值28.9億美元（約新台幣814億元）合約，該合約將為「阿提米絲」計畫（Artemis）打造太空船，NASA原先預期將從這3間公司選擇2間，再進行最後競逐，但未料NASA最後一刻突然改變規則，上週突然宣佈只選擇SpaceX。<br />\n<br />\n對於NASA上述決定，「藍色起源」感到不滿，該公司已在本週一正式向美國政府問責辦公室投訴，指控NASA將合約判給馬斯克SpaceX的決定有瑕玼，存有「高風險」。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克不改其大砲性格，在推特上的「藍色起源」投訴新聞底下留言：「笑死，無法升起（進入軌道）」（&ldquo;Can't get it up （to orbit） lol），除了嘲諷「藍色起源」至今仍未完成任何太空飛行任務外，這句話在美國口語中，還暗指勃起障礙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3512909\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3512909&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oGt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=e30c7d0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3512909&h=f5052cd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3512909</a>"},{"pid":"c3f714270c0b1438158b1f14718faf4c55183056","tid":2506143,"uid":261332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"咁Blue Origin真係廢丫嘛，唔受你玩好合理"},{"pid":"d1dac145da8ad8f781d8369ab91e0e583ded4d4d","tid":2506143,"uid":8113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:27:24.000Z","msg":"賤格  ... 但真係串得起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639f811fb639deb19528ac10bd443837b1a22103","tid":2506143,"uid":103929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1dac145da8ad8f781d8369ab91e0e583ded4d4d","tid":2506143,"ui